==Rhombicosacron==
{{Uniform polyhedra db|Uniform dual polyhedron stat table|rI}}
The [[rhombicosacron]] is a nonconvex [[Isohedral figure|isohedral]] [[polyhedron]]. It is the [[Dual polyhedron|dual]] of the [[nonconvex uniform polyhedron|uniform]] rhombicosahedron, U56. It has 50 [[Vertex (geometry)|vertices]], 120 [[Edge (geometry)|edges]], and 60 [[crossed-quadrilateral]] faces.

